and they now do formation flying as will future helicopters new research will develop control of autonomous planetary rovers using local gps pseudo satellites arl's deep underwater work is done in close cooperation with the monterey bay aquarium research institute last modified wed 25 jan 2012 at 10 21 find a lab or organization stay connected itunes icon google+ icon facebook icon twitter icon linkedin icon stanford university school of engineering 475 via ortega stanford california 94305 4121 650.725 1575 1997 2012 stanford university all rights reserved accreditation info terms of use copyright complaints contact us
